{"tid":2188303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方回應周日9.6九龍遊行　表示將迅速果斷執法適時拘捕","createTime":"2020-09-04T06:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T10:10:19.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f49f8f92f0b5976ed3be7512137c11dafd400522","tid":2188303,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"警方在社交網站表示，留意到網上有人號召星期日在九龍區進行未經批准集結，指絕不容忍任何違法行為，警方部署足夠警力，迅速果斷執法，適時作出拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，參與組織或煽惑他人參與未經批准集結或非法集結，均有可能觸犯《公安條例》，一經定罪最高可被判處監禁5年，有關行為亦會增加病毒在社區傳播的風險，可能違反限聚令。"},{"pid":"03637608fbe6199a705ffdd97e8209b4b2decd2e","tid":2188303,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"將會濫捕"},{"pid":"cbfaedaa0ecb5b39a7cb5cd2a1f072802bc790cf","tid":2188303,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:52:43.000Z","msg":"好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4d74a0d2ec0391bb58061e89b4e996b2029935","tid":2188303,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"簡單講，隨機拘捕<br />\n唔理有無犯法，都要市民負責"},{"pid":"3f73c8d83591581a363b3a105d2ac4b1f17e3f10","tid":2188303,"uid":373809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZM68ikV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZM68ikV.jpg&h=5313a734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n驚你老母 人哋旺角嗰陣日日都咁擺㗎喇<br />\n以後唔撚使去啦咁<br />\n<br />\n9月6 旺角見"},{"pid":"a403b4f2fe085fbdd7a2b9e02fea078d8c9a0c48","tid":2188303,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"好驚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旺角開左咁多次波<br />\n出去既人都未撚驚過"},{"pid":"7d717d1d31b69b2817b05ea59a41f85afe91564d","tid":2188